Title: Project Detroit: OBD-II Manager
Description: A library to parse OBD-II data coming from a vehicle using an ELM323/327 compatible OBD to USB/serial cable.  The solution also includes the WPF Instrument Cluster application that was used in the Project Detroit car!
HomeWiki:
Project Description
A library to parse OBD-II data coming from a vehicle using an ELM323/327 compatible OBD to USB/serial cable. The solution also includes the WPF Instrument Cluster application that was used in the Project Detroit car!

If you have a bug (Issue Report), a needed feature that could benefit everyone (Discussion), or you want to help out (Email), please reach out to us!
